quran[73]{c,v,t}:
  33,1,"Yaa foom Nabiyaama, zoe Wẽnd lɑ f rɑ tũ kɩfen-rãmbã la munaafɩgsã ye, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yaa Mit la bʋʋd-minim Soaba."
  33,2,"Lɑ f tũ b sẽn tɑɑsd foo sẽn yɑɑ sẽn yit f Soɑbã nengẽ wã, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑ tẽng-n-biig ne yãmb sẽn tʋmdã."
  33,3,"Lɑ f bobl f meng ne Wẽnde, lɑ lalld tɑ tεk ne Wẽnde."
  33,4,"Wẽnd kɑ ning sũy ɑ yiib rɑo bɑ a yembr pʋgẽ ye, lɑ A kɑ mɑɑn yãmb pɑgb nins yãmb sẽn yet tɩ b poayã yɑɑ wɑ y mɑ-rãmb poayã tɩ yɑɑ yãmb mɑ-rãmb ye, lɑ A kɑ mɑɑn yãmb kom-yõgdsã tɩ b yɑɑ yãmb koɑmb ye, yɑɑ yãmb noy goɑm lɑ rẽ, lɑ Wẽnd yetɑ sɩdɑ, lɑ Yẽ me n le wilgd sore."
  33,5,"Bool-y-b n tõk ne b bɑɑbã rãmbã, rẽ n yɩɩd tɩrg Wẽnd nengẽ, lɑ yãmb sã n kɑ bãng b bɑɑbã-rãmbã rẽnd b yaa yãmb saam-biisi dĩinã pʋgẽ lɑ yãmb lalldba, lɑ yel kɑ be ne yãmb tɩ y sã n tudg n bool-b n tõk ne zẽng sẽn kɑ b bɑɑbã-rãmbã ye, lɑ yel sẽn be yɑɑ yãmb sẽn mɑɑn pʋ-toog y sũyã pʋsẽ wã, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑ ɑ Lutɑ lɑ ɑ Yoɑlsdɑ."
  33,6,"Nabiyaamã n sõmb ne sɩd kõtbã n yɩɩd b mensã, lɑ ɑ pɑgbã yɑɑ b mɑ-rãmbɑ, lɑ roɑgdbã n sõmb ne tɑɑb n yɩɩdɑ, woto yaa Wẽnd sebrã pʋgɑ, sã n kɑ mikɑme tɩ y rɑt n mɑɑnɑ y lalldbã neere; wãndã yɩɩme n yɑɑ sẽn dɑ gʋls tɩ be sebrã pʋgẽ."
  33,7,"Lɑ tẽeg wakat ning Tõnd sẽn wɑ n deeg Nabiiyaam-rãmbã pʋlengã la D reeg fo pʋlengã lɑ ɑ Nuuh lɑ ɑ Ibrɑɑhɩɩm lɑ ɑ Muusɑ lɑ ɑ Mɑryɑm biig ɑ Iisɑ me nengẽ, lɑ D reeg pʋleng kẽeng b nengẽ, tɩ b pids tẽn-tʋʋmdlmã."
  33,8,"Bʋɩl yĩng lɑ A sok sɩdã-rãmb b sɩdã yelle, lɑ ɑ segl naon-zɑbdg kɩfr-rãmbã yĩngɑ."
  33,9,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdɑ! tẽeg-y Wẽnd neemã wã yãmb zugu, zɑb-zɑbdb sẽn wɑ n nɑ n seg yãmb tɩ Tõnd tʋm sebg lɑ zɑb-zɑbdb yãmb sẽn kɑ ne-b ye, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ net ne yãmb sẽn tʋmdã."
  33,10,"B sẽn wɑ n yi yãmb yĩngr lɑ yãmb tẽngr wεεngẽ n wɑt yãmbɑ, lɑ sɑsɑ ning nin sẽn wɑ n nodg tɩ sũyã be ragsendakẽ, tɩ yãmb sãmbd Wẽnd ne sãmbse."
  33,11,"Beenẽ lɑ b zɑrb sɩd-kõtbã n ges lɑ b miim-b miuun-kεgengɑ."
  33,12,"Lɑ sɑsɑ ning munaafɩgsã lɑ neb nins bãas sẽn be b sũyẽ wã sẽn wɑ n yetdẽ: ""Wẽnd kɑ pʋlem tõnd rẽndɑ belgr bɑlɑ""."
  33,13,"Lɑ sɑsɑ ning b sãndɑ sẽn wɑ n yeele: ""yaa yãmb Yɑsrib (Mɑdĩin) rãmbɑ yɑlsg zĩig kɑe y yĩng dε! Pĩnd n lebg-y; tɩ b sãndɑ kot Nabiyaamã sor n yetdẽ: ""ɑd tõnd zɑgsã kɑ tɑr gũudb ye"". Lɑ b zɑgsã yɑool n tɑr gũudba, kɑ ba fʋɩ n zʋʋg zoees bɑl lɑ b rɑt ye."
  33,14,"Lɑ tɩ b (bɛɛbã) sã n da tõe n tũ (tẽngã) kɩrems n kẽ, rẽ poorẽ tɩ b yeel-b tɩ b mɑɑn lɑgem-n-tɑɑre, b ra nɑ mɑɑn-ɑ, tɩ rẽnda meng yaa yol-yol ne-ba."
  33,15,"Lɑ b yɑool n dɑ pʋlmɑ Wẽnd pĩnda, tɩ b kɑ nɑ n zoe ye, lɑ Wẽnd pʋlengã yɑɑ bũmb ning b sẽn nɑ n soke."
  33,16,"Yeele: ""zoees kɑ nɑ n tɑll yõod ne yãmb bɑ tɩ yãmb sã n zoe n nɑ n põs kũumã mɑɑ kʋʋbã ye, lɑ bɑ tɩ y põs me, y kõon n vʋɩɩm noog rẽndɑ bilf bɑlɑ''."
  33,17,"Yeele: ""ãnd n tõe n põsg yãmb n yi Wẽnd t'A sã n dɑt yãmb ne wẽng ma t'A sã n rɑt yãmb ne yolsgo?"" Lɑ b kɑ nɑ n pɑɑm lɑlld lɑ sõɑngd tɩ kɑ Wẽnd ye."
  33,18,"Ad Wẽnd mii koɑmesdbã sẽn be yãmb pʋgẽ wã lɑ neb nins sẽn yet b sɑɑm-biisã: ""wa-y tõnd nengẽ wã"". Lɑ b yɑool n kɑ sɑk n nɑ n kẽ keelmã (zɑbrã) pʋgẽ rẽndɑ bilf bɑlɑ."
  33,19,"B sẽn maan beem yãmb zug yĩnga, lɑ rɑbeemã sã n wɑ fo neeme tɩ b get foo tɩ b ninã yilimd wɑlɑ kũum sẽn yilimd ɑ soabɑ, lɑ rɑbeemã sã n looge b sɩlgdɑ yãmb ne zɩlmɑ sẽn zɑbde, n mɑɑn yã-beed n rɑt sõmbã (arzεgsã b sẽn pɑɑm bεεbẽ wã), bãmb rãmb lɑ sẽn kɑ kõ sɩd tɩ Wẽnd sãɑm b tʋʋmã, lɑ wãndã yɩɩme n yɑɑ nɑɑnɑ ne Wẽnde."
  33,20,"B sãmbdɑme tɩ zãmã wã nɑn kɑ loog ye, lɑ zãmã wã sã n lebg n wɑ, b mɑɑndɑ nonglem n dɑg n beẽ weoogẽ dãmbã pʋgẽ n sokd yãmb yelle, lɑ bɑ tɩ b sã n dɑ pɑ yãmb pʋgẽ wã me, b kɑ nɑ n kẽ zɑbrẽ wã rẽndɑ bilf bɑlɑ."
  33,21,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, ad togs-n-tɑ-sõng zĩndɑ Wẽnd Tẽn-tʋmdã vɩɩmã pʋgẽ yãmb yĩngɑ, ned ning sẽn tẽed-ɑ Wẽnd lɑ Yɑoolem dɑɑrã lɑ ɑ tẽeg Wẽnd yell wʋsgo."
  33,22,"Lɑ sɩd kõɑtbã sẽn wɑ n yã zãmã wã, b yeelɑme: ""yɑɑ wã lɑ Wẽnd ne A Tẽn-tʋʋmã sẽn pʋlem tõndã, lɑ Wẽnd la A Tẽn-tʋʋmã pʋlenã yi sɩdɑ"". Lɑ rẽ kɑ pɑɑs-b rẽndɑ sɩd-kũun lɑ sɑk-n-tũ."
  33,23,"Neb n zĩnd sɩd-kõtbã pʋgẽ n pids b sẽn pʋlengã ne Wẽndã, lɑ be b pʋgẽ sẽn mɑɑn kɑɑlem, lɑ be b pʋgẽ sẽn nɑ gũudɑ, lɑ b kɑ tol n teem bɑ bilf ye."
  33,24,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ Wẽnd rol sɩdã-rãmb b sɩdã yĩngɑ, lɑ A nɑms munaafɩgsã t'A sã n dɑtɑ, mɑɑ t'A sɑk n deeg b tuubgã, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ yaafd lɑ yoɑlsdɑ."
  33,25,"Lɑ Wẽnd lebsɑ kɩfr-rãmbã ne b sũ-yikrã, b kɑ pɑɑm bɑ fʋɩ, lɑ Wẽnd sekɑ sɩd-kõɑtbã n yi zɑbrã, lɑ Wẽnd yɑɑ pãng-soɑb lɑ zɩslem-soɑbɑ."
  33,26,"Lɑ A sik Yahuud-rãmb nins sẽn sõng kɩrf-rãmbã b gũudmã zɑgs pʋsẽ, lɑ A kẽes b sũyẽ wã rɑbeem, tɩ yãmb kʋʋd b sãndɑ lɑ y yõgd b sãndɑ."
  33,27,"Lɑ A leds yãmb b tẽngẽ wã lɑ b zɑgsẽ wã lɑ b ɑrzεgsẽ wã. La yãmb nao sẽn nɑn kɑ tɑg tẽng ningã, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ bũmb fãɑ tõogdɑ."
  33,28,"Yaa foom Nabiyaama! Yeel f pɑgbã: ""Sã n mikɑme tɩ yãmb rɑtɑ dũni vɩɩmã lɑ ɑ nɑg-teedã, bɩ y wɑ tɩ m kõ-y kũun tɩ tɑ y yɑm lɑ m bɑs-y bɑsg sẽn be neere,"
  33,29,"Lɑ sã n mikɑme tɩ yãmb rɑtɑ Wẽnd lɑ A Tẽn-tʋʋmã lɑ yɑoolem zɑkã bɩ y bãng tɩ Wẽnd seglɑ rol-kẽeng n bĩng yɑɑ b mɑnegdb yãmb pʋgẽ wã""."
  33,30,"Yaa yãmb Nabiyaam pagba! Ned ningɑ sẽn wa-a ne yel-wẽnd vẽenegɑ b fãoodɑ naongã naoor ɑ yiib ɑ yĩngɑ, lɑ rẽ me yɩɩme n yɑɑ nɑɑnɑ ne Wẽnde."
  33,31,"Lɑ yãmb pʋgẽ wã ned ning sẽn wõr ɑ meng lɑ ɑ tʋm tʋʋm-sõmɑ, D kõt-ɑ-lɑ ɑ rolbã noor ɑ yiibu, lɑ D segl rɩtl wɑgell ɑ yĩngɑ."
  33,32,"Yaa yãmb Nabiyaam pagbã! Ad yãmb kɑ wɑla pɑg buudã fãɑ dε! Ad yãmb sã n zoe Wẽnde, bɩ y rɑ noos y koees tɩ ned ning bãɑg sẽn be ɑ sũurẽ wɑ mɑɑn yɑm-leoog ye, lɑ y gom mɑnegr goɑm sẽn pɑ tɑr sik ye."
  33,33,"Lɑ y tɑbend y zɑgsã pʋse, lɑ y rɑ yi wɑlɑ rẽenem zɩɩlem yiibã buud ye, lɑ y yɑls ne Pʋʋsg lɑ y kõ ɑrzεk-yɩlgr-pʋɩɩrã (Zɑkã), lɑ y tũ Wẽnd lɑ A Tẽn-tʋʋmã, Wẽnd sẽn dɑtã yɑɑ sẽn nɑ loog ne rẽok bʋʋd fãɑ n bɑs yãmb ɑ zɑkã rãmbɑ lɑ ɑ yɩlg yãmb sõmɑ."
  33,34,"Lɑ y tẽeg Wẽnd goamã la Bʋʋd-welgr sẽn kɑremd yãmb zɑgsã pʋsẽ wã, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ Bʋg-bʋg soɑb ne yãmbɑ n yɑɑ minim Tẽng-n-biigɑ."
  33,35,"Ad lɩslaam rɑɑdã lɑ lɩslaam pogsã, lɑ sɩd-kõɑtb rɑɑdã lɑ sɩd-kõɑtb pogsã, lɑ wõr-m-meng rɑɑdã lɑ wõr-m-meng pogsã, lɑ sɩd-toagsdb rɑɑdã lɑ sɩd-toagsdb pogsã, lɑ sug-maandb rɑɑdã lɑ sug-maandb pogsã, lɑ (Wẽnd) yεεsdbb raadã lɑ (Wẽnd) yεεsdb pogsã, lɑ sãrã-mɑɑndb rɑɑdã lɑ sãrã-mɑɑndb pogsã, lɑ no-loεtb rɑɑdã lɑ no-loεtb pogsã, lɑ gũus-m-tɑoor raadã lɑ gũus-m-tɑoor pogsã, lɑ (Wẽnd) tẽegdb rɑɑdã wʋsgã lɑ (Wẽnd) tẽegdb pogsã, ɑd Wẽnd seglɑ yaafg lɑ rolb sẽn yɑɑ kẽeng b yĩngɑ."
  33,36,"Lɑ kɑ segd ne sɩd-kõɑt rɑoog lɑ sɩd-kõɑt-poɑk tɩ Wẽnd lɑ A Tẽn-tʋʋmã sã n gãneg yell bʋʋd n sε bɩ b le tɑll yɑm-yãkr b yellã pʋgẽ ye, lɑ ned ning sẽn kɩɩs-ɑ Wẽnd lɑ A Tẽn-tʋʋmã rẽnd ɑ menemɑ meneng sẽn yɑɑ vẽenegɑ."
  33,37,"(Lɑ tẽeg sɑsɑ ning) fo sẽn wɑ n yet fo sẽn mɑɑn-ɑ soɑb neer tɩ Wẽnd mɑɑn-ɑ neerã: ""tɑll f pɑgã lɑ f zoe Wẽnde"". Lɑ fo solgd f mengẽ wã yell ningɑ Wẽnd sẽn nɑ n vẽneg-ɑ, lɑ fo zoet nebã, lɑ yɑool n yɑɑ Wẽnd lɑ fo sõmb n zoe. Lɑ a Zɑyd sẽn wɑ n bɑs pɑgã, Tõnd kẽes-ɑ-lɑ kãɑdem pʋgẽ (Tõnd loe-ɑ-lɑ fur) n kõ foo, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ yell rɑ zĩnd sɩd-kõɑtbã yĩng b kom-yõgdsã pɑgbã pʋgẽ, tɩ b sã n bɑs-bɑ tɩ bãmb wẽneg n nɑ n furb-bɑ, lɑ Wẽnd yel-rɑtmã yɑɑ bũmb sẽn yɩt tɩlɑe."
  33,38,"Yel kɑe ne Nabiyaamã, Wẽnd sẽn kõ-a sor yell ning pʋgẽ ye; yɑɑ Wẽnd yell sẽn dɑ sɩng n beẽ sẽn loog-b pĩndã zugu, lɑ Wẽnd yel-dɑtmã yɑɑ sẽn korde tɩ nɑ n yɩ tɩlɑe."
  33,39,"Tẽn-tʋʋm kãnsã tɑɑsdɑ Wẽnd tẽn-tʋmdã lɑ b zoet-A lɑ b kɑ zoet ned ba ɑ ye sã n kɑ Wẽnde, lɑ Wẽnd geelgã A yemsã tʋʋmã sek yã."
  33,40,"A Mohɑmmɑd kɑ yɩ n yɑɑ yãmb roɑpã ba a yembr bɑɑbɑ ye, lɑ sẽn be bɑlɑ, a yɑɑ Wẽnd Tẽn-tʋʋm n yɑɑ Nabiyaam-rãmbɑ pidsdɑ, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ mit ne bũmb fãɑ."
  33,41,"Yãmb ɑ sẽn kõb sɩdɑ! Tẽeg-y Wẽnde (yʋʋrã/yelle), tẽegr sẽn wɑooge."
  33,42,"Lɑ y yɩlg-A yibeoog lɑ zɑɑbre."
  33,43,"Yẽndɑ n yolsd yãmbɑ lɑ A pẽgd-yã, t'A Mɑlεk-rãmbɑ me kot Wẽnd n kõt yãmbɑ sẽn nɑ yɩl t'A yiis yãmb ligsẽ wã n kẽng vẽenmẽ wã, lɑ A yɩɩme n yɑɑ yoɑlsdɑ ne sɩd-kõɑtbã."
  33,44,"B sẽn nɑ n sεg-A rɑɑrã b pʋʋsem yɑɑ Tɩlgre, lɑ A segla rol-wɑgell b yĩngɑ."
  33,45,"Foom ɑ Tẽn-tʋʋma! Ad Tõnd tʋma foom tɩ fo yɑɑ kaset-soɑbɑ lɑ sũ-noɑɑgdɑ lɑ bugsdɑ,"
  33,46,"Lɑ boɑɑnd n tʋgd Wẽnd nengẽ ne A rɑɑbo, lɑ fɩtl sẽn yɑɑ vẽenem."
  33,47,"Lɑ f noog sɩd-kõɑtbã sũuri tɩ yɩɩdlem kẽeng sẽn yi Wẽnd nengẽ be b yĩngɑ."
  33,48,"Lɑ f rɑ tũ kɩrf-rãmbã la munaafɩgsã ye, lɑ f rɑ wẽnemd n ges b sẽn nɑmsd foo wã ye, lɑ f bobl f meng ne Wẽnde, lɑ ɑd bobend tɑ tεk tɩ sã n yɑɑ Wẽnde."
  33,49,"Yãmb ɑ sẽn kõb sɩdɑ! Y sã n kẽ kãadem ne sɩd-kõt-pogsã rẽ poorẽ n bɑs-bɑ tɑoor tɩ yãmb nɑn kɑ kẽ ne-bɑ, bɩ y bãng tɩ b ka tɑr rɑsem-rãmb sõore b sẽn nɑ n zĩnd n gũ ye; bɩ y kõ-b kũun tɩ tɑ b yɑm, lɑ y bɑs-b bɑsg sẽn be neere."
  33,50,"Foom a Nabiyaama! Ad Tõnd kõo foo sor ne fo pɑgb nins fo sẽn kõ-b b furã ligdi, lɑ D le kõ-f sor tɩ f tõe n kẽ kãɑdem ne fo nug sẽn sooge ( yemb pogsã) sẽn yɑɑ Wẽnd sẽn n kõ foomã, lɑ f bɑɑbɑ kãseng lɑ f bɑɑbɑ-bil kom-pugli, lɑ f pʋgdb-rãmb kom-pugli, lɑ f yεsb kom-pugli, lɑ f mɑ tõp-pogs kom-pugli nins b sẽn maan higra nɑɑg foomã (n yik n wãag n bɑs b tẽngã), lɑ pɑg sẽn yɑɑ sɩd-kõɑt sẽn dɩk-ɑ meng n kõ Nabiyaam tɩ Nabiyaamã sã n dɑt n kẽe kãɑdem ne-ɑ sɑkdɑ me t'ɑ loe-ɑ furi, lɑ rẽ welgɑ ne foog f yembr bɑlɑ, sɩd kõt-rɑɑd ɑ tɑɑbã(Mũumin-dãmbɑ) kɑ nɑɑg be ye, Tõnd bãngɑ Tõnd sẽn dogl-b yεl nins-bɑ b pɑgbẽ wã (pɑ tõe n zʋʋg nɑɑs ye) lɑ b nusã sẽn so pɑgb ninsã yεlã pʋgẽ, Tõnd mɑɑnɑ woto bʋɩl yĩng lɑ weoogr rɑ pɑɑm foo ye, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yaa Yaafd n yaa Yolsda."
  33,51,"Fo tõe n lɑk n bɑsɑ f sẽn dɑt-ɑ soɑb f pɑgbã pʋga, lɑ f pẽnegd f sẽn dɑt-ɑ soɑbɑ; lɑ fo sẽn dɑt n pẽneg-ɑ soɑb fo sẽn dɑ lɑk n bɑs-b rãmbã pʋgẽ wã yell kɑ ne f ye; rẽndɑ n pẽ ne b nin nɑ mɑɑg lɑ b sũy kõn sãame, lɑ fo sẽn kõ-b yemkãm fãɑ bũmb ning me le tɑ b yɑm; lɑ Wẽnd mii sẽn be yãmb sũyã pʋsẽ, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ Bãngd n yɑɑ Bʋgbʋg-soɑbɑ."
  33,52,"Pɑgb ɑ tɑɑb kɑ segd ne foo bãmbã loogr poor ye, lɑ f leb n kɑ tõe n tedg-b ne pɑgb ɑ tɑɑb me bɑ tɩ b sõmblemã taa fo yɑm, sɑ n kɑ fo nug sẽn sooge (yemb pogsã), lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ bũmb fãɑ Gũusdɑ."
  33,53,"Yãmb ɑ neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdɑ!, rɑ kẽ-y Nabiyaamã zɑgsẽ wã sã n kɑ b kõo yãmb sor tɩ kẽ n rɩ ye, lɑ y rɑɑ wɑ zĩnd n gũud-ɑ ye, lɑ b sã n bool-y bɩ y kẽ, lɑ y sã n dɩ n sε bɩ y sãeeg lɑ y rɑ yɑɑs n sõs n lolem yɑm ye, ɑd rẽ rɑ nɑmsdɑ Nabiyaamã t'ɑ yɑool n zoet yãnd ne yãmbɑ, lɑ Wẽnd kɑ zoet yãnd ne sɩd vẽnegr ye, lɑ yãmb sã n dɑt n sok Nɑbiyɑɑmɑ pɑgbã bũmb yelle, bɩ y sok-b lill poore, rẽnd n yɩɩd yɩlgr yãmb ne bãmb sũyẽ wã, lɑ kɑ segd ne yãmb tɩ y mɑɑn sẽn nɑ nɑms Wẽnd Tẽn-tʋʋmã ye, lɑ kɑ segd ne-y me tɩ y kẽ kãadem ne ɑ pɑgbã ɑ loogr poor ye, ɑd rẽndɑ yɩɩme n yɑɑ zũnuub-kẽeng Wẽnd nengẽ."
  33,54,"Yãmb sɑ n vẽneg bũmb bɩ y soɑlg-ɑ lɑme, ad Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑɑ bũmb fãɑ Mitɑ."
  33,55,"Yell kɑ be ne pɑgbã tɩ ned yãb-ɑ lɑ ɑ gom neba tɩ pɑ tũ ne lill ye, tɩ sã n yɑɑ b bɑɑbɑ-rãmbã, lɑ b koɑmbã, lɑ b tãopã, lɑ b tãopã koɑmbã, lɑ b tão-pogsã koɑmbã, lɑ b pog-tɑɑsã, lɑ b nusã sẽn soogã ( b yemsã), lɑ y zoe Wẽnde, bɑlɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑ bũmbɑ fãɑ Sεεta."
  33,56,"Ad Wẽnd ne A Malεgsã pʋʋsda Nabiyaamã, yãmb ɑ neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdɑ! pʋʋs-y-yã-a lɑ y kos tɩlgr sẽn yɑɑ kẽoog n kõ-a."
  33,57,"Ad sẽn mɑɑnd-b tɩ nɑmsd Wẽnd la A Tẽn-tʋʋmã, Wẽnd kãɑbd-b lɑme Dũni kaanẽ la Laahre, lɑ A segl naon-fɑɑgdg b yĩngɑ."
  33,58,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn nɑmsd-b muumin rɑɑdã lɑ muumin pogsã tɩ b yaool n ka maan ba fʋɩ wã, ad b tʋkɑ zĩri lɑ yel-wẽnd sẽn yɑɑ vẽenegɑ."
  33,59,"Yaa foom Nabiyaama! Yeel f pɑgbã lɑ f kom-pugli wã lɑ muumin-rãmbã pɑgbã, tɩ b woglg b fʋ-bεdã n mɑɑn tɩ kɩll n pẽnege, tɩ rẽnd n pẽ ne b nɑ bãng-ba, n kɑ mɑɑn tɩ naong tɑ-b ye, lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n ya Yaafd n yaa Yolsdɑ."
  33,60,"Lɑ tɩ munaafɩgsã la bãag sẽn be neb nins sũyẽ wã la zũngdbã sẽn be Madiinã sã n kɑ tek n bɑse, D nɑ n kɩtame tɩ fo zab ne-ba, rẽ poorẽ, b kõn zĩnd ne foo Mɑdĩinɑ rẽndɑ sɑsɑ bilf bɑlɑ."
  33,61,"Tɩ b yɑɑ b sẽn digd-b rãmb n zãɑg ne yolsgo, b sẽn be zĩig ning fãɑ, b yõgd-b lɑme n kʋʋd sõmɑ."
  33,62,"Yɑɑ Wẽnd sẽn maan tɩ deng tɑoorã to-to wã, lɑ fo kɑ nɑ n pɑɑm Wẽnd mɑnesmã toeeng ye."
  33,63,"Nebã sokdɑ foom Sɑsã wã yelle (Dĩnã Yikrã), yeele: ''Ad a bãngrã yɑɑ Wẽnd nengẽ bɑl lɑ be, lɑ ãndã n wĩnigd foom tɩ Sɑsã wã kɑ pẽnege?''"
  33,64,"Ad Wẽnd kãaba kɩfr-rãmbã lɑ A seglg Bugum b yĩngɑ."
  33,65,"B yɑɑ ɑ pʋgẽ wã pɑɑdbɑ, lɑ b kɑ nɑ n tol n pɑɑm lɑlld lɑ sõngd ye."
  33,66,"Raɑr ning b sẽn nɑ n leebd b nemsã bugmẽ wã tɩ b yetdẽ: "" Kato, tõnd sã n dɑ tũẽ Wẽnd la A Tẽn-tʋʋmã pɑ são""."
  33,67,"Tɩ b yetẽ: ""d Soɑbɑ! Ad tõnd tũu d zu-sob-n-dãmbã lɑ d nin-bεdã tɩ b menes tõnd sorã,"
  33,68,"D Soɑbɑ! Kõ-b naong sẽn fãoog n pɑɑse, lɑ F kãɑb-b kãab-bedre""."
  33,69,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdɑ! Rɑ yɩ-y wala neb nins sẽn nɑms ɑ Muusɑ wã ye, tɩ Wẽnd tɩlg-ɑ n yi b sẽn dõd-ɑ wã. Lɑ ɑ yɩɩme n yɑɑ wɑgell Wẽnd nengẽ."
  33,70,"Yaa yãmb neb nins sẽn kõ sɩdɑ! Zoe-y Wẽnd lɑ y yeel gom-tɩrse."
  33,71,"T'A nɑ mɑneg yãmb tʋʋmã, lɑ A yaaf yãmb yel-wẽnɑ, la ned ning sẽn tũ Wẽnd lɑ A Tẽn-tʋʋmã, sɩd la hakɩɩka a tɩlgɑ tɩlg-kẽengɑ."
  33,72,"Ad Tõnd yeela sɑɑsã lɑ tẽngã lɑ tãmsã tɩ b reeg Bobelle, tɩ b zãgs-a la b yet tɩ yɩɩdɑ b pãnga, b kɑ nɑ n tõog ye; tɩ ninsɑɑl tʋk-a, ad ɑ yɩɩ wẽgd ne mengã n yɑɑ zɩta."
  33,73,"Bʋɩl yĩng lɑ A nɑms munaafɩgsã la munaafɩg-pogsã la lagem-n-ta rapã la lagem-ta pogsã, la Wẽnd sɑk n deeg sɩd-kõt-rɑɑdã lɑ sɩd-kõt-pogsã tuubgu. Lɑ Wẽnd yɩɩme n yɑ Yaafda n yɑɑ Yolsdɑ."
